@FabrizioRomano on Szoboszlai: &ldquo;Many clubs are interested but you don&rsquo;t have to negotiate with the club [Salzburg], pay the clause, &euro;25m. Now it&rsquo;s time to convince the player. He wants to play, to be a starter always. About Arsenal, probably he would be a starter today.&rdquo; #afc<br />
<br />
@FabrizioRomano on Szoboszlai: &ldquo;Arsenal are scouting him for many years, they are in contact with his agent, they want to bring some quality to their midfield, they are in a difficult moment so they need this kind of magic in midfield, this kind of skilful player.&rdquo; #afc<br />
<br />
@FabrizioRomano : &ldquo;Next week, we will have the final decision from Dominik Szoboszlai. We will see if it will be Arsenal, Leipzig - the easiest solution because they&rsquo;re in the same family with Red Bull - also interest from AC Milan, they are always in contact.&rdquo; [ @podcastherewego ]<br />
